twcore.core.net
Class SSEncryption

java.lang.Object
  twcore.core.net.SSEncryption

public class SSEncryption
extends java.lang.Object

Subspace encryption class. For the vast majority of uses of TWCore, the understanding of this class is completely unnecessary. It can be ignored simply as a black box that encrypts and decrypts packets as needed. A key is randomly generated by the client, which is sent to the server as a special core packet (0x01), and the server returns a key based on this (in core packet 0x02). An encryption table is then generated from the server key, which is applied with the server key to encrypt/decrypt packets.
